th, in fact, with the US-based data plan. And they offer plans for other countries as well that include anywhere from 1GB to 4GB per month, so you can pick the ones that best suit your needs.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you do a lot of traveling for work, then <a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://shop.macworld.com/sales/instabridge-esim-usa-lifetime-plan-2-gb-month?utm_source=macworld.com&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_campaign=instabridge-esim-usa-lifetime-plan-2-gb-month&amp;utm_term=scsf-567445&amp;utm_content=a0x1P0000058XwIQAU&amp;scsonar=1&amp;xcust=1-1-1671192-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">Instabridge eSim</a> is a must-have. And since you can get lifetime subscriptions to any of their plans this week for just $149 during our Spring Digital Blowout — no coupon codes required — it’s definitely economical.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://shop.macworld.com/sales/instabridge-esim-usa-lifetime-plan-2-gb-month?utm_source=macworld.com&amp;utm_medium=referral-cta&amp;utm_campaign=instabridge-esim-usa-lifetime-plan-2-gb-month&amp;utm_term=scsf-567445&amp;utm_content=a0x1P0000058XwIQAU&amp;scsonar=1&amp;xcust=1-1-1671192-1-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\"> </a></p>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://cdnp1.stackassets.com/61d06c33d5ca61416103dc78fcc61459f8592998/store/af699063b298018e61964b86efb79fcf12943d05d67977a3bfa1330ef996/sale_320898_primary_image.jpg\" alt loading=\"lazy\" /></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Instabridge eSIM: Lifetime Plan – $149</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://shop.macworld.com/sales/instabridge-esim-usa-lifetime-plan-2-gb-month?utm_source=macworld.com&amp;utm_medium=referral-cta&amp;utm_campaign=instabridge-esim-usa-lifetime-plan-2-gb-month&amp;utm_term=scsf-567445&amp;utm_content=a0x1P0000058XwIQAU&amp;scsonar=1&amp;xcust=1-1-167119